      <h2>Results</h2>
      <p>
        The system launched on 2026-02-11 with 9/9 launch criteria met. All 8 organs are operational.<Cite id={13} author="Deming, W. Edwards" title="Out of the Crisis" source="MIT Press" year={1986} /> Deming's quality management principles — measure, validate, improve — are embedded in the monthly audit cycle. 228 validation checks pass across the Platinum validation suite, covering CI workflow presence, CHANGELOG files, architectural decision records, badge rows, and implementation status fields for every repo. POSSE distribution is live (Mastodon + Discord). Jekyll/GitHub Pages publishes 10 meta-system essays (~40K words) with an Atom RSS feed.
      </p>

